{
  "texts": [
    "The gold standard of final diagnosis was the consensus of an independent cardiology expert panel with 20 years of clinical service experience following Chest Pain Management Guidelines 38, 60, 61.",
    "This panel had full access to patient records and cardiovascular lab test results, ensuring a comprehensive and authoritative standard for comparison.",
    "The definitive diagnosis for cases where there was uncertainty was established using Voting Mechanisms.",
    "(Figure 1)",
    "The statistical analysis in this study was conducted using the SPSS 27.0 statistical package for Windows, Python version 3.8, and R software version 4.2.2, provided by the R Foundation for Statistical Computing."
  ]
}